**Terms and Conditions for Online Ticket Booking – Sky Voyagers
**1. Acceptance of Terms:** By using the online ticket booking services provided by [Airline Name], you agree to abide by these Terms and Conditions. Please read them carefully before making a reservation.
**2. Booking Process:** a. The online ticket booking system is available 24/7, subject to scheduled maintenance periods. b. Passengers must provide accurate and complete information during the booking process. c. Booking confirmation will be sent to the provided email address.
**3. Payment:** a. Payment must be made in full at the time of booking. b. [Airline Name] accepts major credit/debit cards and other specified payment methods. c. Prices are subject to change based on availability and other factors.
**4. Ticket Cancellation and Refund:** a. Cancellation requests must be made through the online platform or by contacting [Airline Name] customer support. b. Refund eligibility is subject to the fare rules of the purchased ticket. c. Refunds will be processed in accordance with [Airline Name]'s refund policy.
**5. Flight Changes:** a. Changes to flight details may be allowed, subject to availability and applicable fees. b. Changes must be made through the online platform or by contacting [Airline Name] customer support.
**6. Baggage Policy:** a. Passengers are subject to [Airline Name]'s baggage policy, including weight and size restrictions. b. Additional fees may apply for excess baggage.
**7. Check-in and Boarding:** a. Passengers are responsible for checking in within the specified time frame. b. Boarding gates close a certain time before departure, and late arrivals may result in denied boarding.
**8. Travel Documents:** a. Passengers must possess valid travel documents, including passports and visas, as required. b. [Airline Name] is not responsible for any issues arising from inadequate travel documentation.
**9. Force Majeure:** a. [Airline Name] shall not be liable for any delay, cancellation, or failure to perform its obligations due to unforeseen circumstances or force majeure events.
**10. Privacy and Data Security:** a. [Airline Name] respects passenger privacy and complies with applicable data protection laws. b. Personal information collected during the booking process will be used in accordance with [Airline Name]'s Privacy Policy.
**11. Governing Law:** These Terms and Conditions are governed by the laws of [Jurisdiction]. Any disputes shall be resolved in the courts of [Jurisdiction].
**12. Amendments:** [Airline Name] reserves the right to amend these Terms and Conditions at any time. Changes will be effective upon posting on the website.
By using our online ticket booking services, you acknowledge and agree to these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree, please do not proceed with the booking.
